{"tid":654911,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"五月天怪獸是唔是華人最強結他手","createTime":"2018-05-06T05:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T18:12:29.000Z","uid":106675,"like":8,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"57fd1842c01a644a4d4155177b6212b4695413e7","tid":654911,"uid":106675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:18:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ParsonsBandClub/videos/1617994664938680/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FParsonsBandClub%2Fvideos%2F1617994664938680%2F&d=sGwUIirdB4qypkm10ixhJsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=11013510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ParsonsBandClub/videos/1617994664938680/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGibson發行的首把華語藝人簽名款結他，在美國Nashville Gibson Custom Shop手工製造，結他整體製作及美術總監由怪獸親自擔任。在Gibson Custom 1960復刻版Les Paul基礎上加入怪獸親自設計的「金色獨角獸」及其指定的琴頸形狀、Burstbucker-2開放式斑馬Neck Pickup、Burstbucker-3金色封閉式Bridge Pickup，顏色為Monster Red Burst，配置特製的怪獸款式結他盒。怪獸表示：「在音樂的路上，結他是我的夥伴，獨角獸的Logo象徵一種溫柔的守護、戰鬥的勇氣與發自靈魂深處的音樂。」依從怪獸本人現時演出使用之結他，絕對忠實五迷必有之選！<br />\n<br />\n原價 $57,999<br />\n五月限定搖滾價 $45,000<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efc5698f01d35ab97fa9c45a616485cf87e280b","tid":654911,"uid":31314,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:23:03.000Z","msg":"問過謝霆鋒未？"},{"pid":"ffeb539d8bd3e93bfc5421b0eb32e5d65407943b","tid":654911,"uid":180035,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:23:19.000Z","msg":"侮辱左Les Paul<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514b32f9e369467cef0b01ffa52d778c221c20bf","tid":654911,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T05:25:28.000Z","msg":"喼神唔係破產啦咩"},{"pid":"726a646e90c88f680b55cbe81c3f427123baa192","tid":654911,"uid":106675,"like":3,"disli